name: Hanalai Meltdown
description: An aerial view of Hanalei, Kauai, HI. This image was made as part of my work documenting the different kind of rainforests in Kauai. It’s my favourite image from all of my aerial images shot in Hanalei. For me, it completely encapsulates the fragile beauty of this unique place. (Dimensions: 6412x3794) (JPEG Size: 7 MB)
